: null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000557, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O God, I seek refuge in Thee from the agitation of craving, the violence of wrath, the domination of envy, the frailty of patience, the lack of contentment, surliness of character, urgency of passion, the disposition to vehemence, following caprice, opposing guidance, the sleep of heedlessness, undertaking the toilsome, preferring falsehood over truth, persisting in sin.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Allah! Mai Tujh se panah maangta hu hirs o laalach ke zor, ghaiz o ghazab ki shiddat, hasad ki aag, be-sabri, bharose ki kami, bad-akhlaaqi, khwaaish'e nafs ki ziyaadati, taassub o nafrat ka ghalba, khwahishaat'e nafsaani ki pairawi, hidaayat ki mukhaalefat, ghaflat bhari zindagi aur takalluf pasanda se aur baatil ko haq par tarjeeh dene, gunaho’n par gunah karne.", "Urdu": "اے اللہ!میں تجھ سے پناہ مانگتا ہوں حرص کی طغیانی،غضب کی شدت، حسد کی چیرہ دستی، بے صبری، قناعت کی کمی، کج اخلاقی، خواہش نفس کی فراوانی، عصبیت کے غلبہ، ہوا وہوس کی پیروی، ہدایت کی خلاف ورزی، خواب غفلت (کی مدہوشی ) اورتکلف پسندی سے نیز باطل کو حق پر ترجیح دینے، گناہوں پر اصرار کرنے۔", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَعُوْذُ بِكَ مِنْ هَيَجَانِ الْحِرْصِ وَسَوْرَةِ الْغَضَبِ وَغَلَبَةِ الْحَسَدِ وَضَعْفِ الصَّبْرِ وَقِلَّةِ الْقَنَاعَةِ وَشَكَاسَةِ الْخُلُقِ وَاِلْحَاحِ الشَّهْوَةِ وَمَلَكَةِ الْحَمِيَّةِ وَمُتَابَعَةِ الْهَوٰى وَمُخَالَفَةِ اِلْهُدٰى وَسِنَةِ الْغَفْلَةِ وَتَعَاطِي الْكُلْفَةِ وَاِيْثَارِ الْبَاطِلِ عَلَى الْحَقِّ وَالْاِصْرَارِ عَلَى الْمَاْثَمِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1001649, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Making little of disobedience, making much of obedience, vying with the wealthy, disparaging the poor, guarding badly over those in our hands, failing to thank those who have done good to us, aiding a wrongdoer, abandoning someone troubled, wanting what is not rightfully ours, and speaking about knowledge without knowing.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Maasiyat ko halka aur ita’at ko azeem samajh ne, daulat-mando’n ke saamne fakhr, mohtaajo’n ko haqeer aur apne zer'e nazar kaam karne waalo’n ki buri dekh-bhaal aur jo ham se bhalaayi kare uski na-shukri se aur isse ke ham kisi zaalim ki madad kare aur museebat-zadah ki taraf nazr na kare ya is cheez ka iraada kare jiska hamein haq nahi ya deen mein be-samajhe-buje dakhal de.", "Urdu": "معصیت کو حقیر اوراطاعت کو عظیم سمجھنے، دولت مندوں کے سے تفاخر، محتاجوں کی تحقیر اوراپنے زیر دستوں کی بری نگہداشت اورجو ہم سے بھلائی کرے اس کی ناشکری سے اوراس سے کہ ہم کسی ظالم کی مدد کریں اورمصیبت زدہ کو نظر انداز کریں یا اس چیز کا قصد کریں جس کا ہمیں حق نہیں یا دین میں نے جانے بوجھے دخل دیں۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَاسْتِصْغَارِ الْمَعْصِيَةِ وَاسْتِكْبَارِ الطَّاعَةِ وَمُبَاهَاةِ الْمُكْثِرِيْنَ وَالْاِزْرَاۗءِ بِالْمُقِلِّيْنَ وَسُوْءِ الْوِلَايَةِ لِمَنْ تَحْتَ اَيْدِيْنَا وَتَرْكِ الشُّكْرِ لِمَنِ اصْطَنَعَ الْعَارِفَةَ عِنْدَنَا اَوْ اَنْ نَعْضُدَ ظَالِمًا اَوْ نَخْذُلَ مَلْهُوْفًا اَوْ نَرُوْمَ مَا لَيْسَ لَنَا بِحَقٍّ اَوْ نَقُوْلَ فِي الْعِلْمِ بِغَيْرِ عِلْمٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1001650, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "We seek refuge in Thee from harbouring dishonesty toward anyone, being pleased with our works, and stretching out our expectations. We seek refuge in Thee from ill-mindedness, looking down on the small, Satan’s gaining mastery over us, time’s afflicting us, and the sovereign’s oppressing us. We seek refuge in Thee from acting with prodigality and not having sufficiency.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ham Tujh se panah maangte hai is baat se keh kisi ko dhoka dene ka iraada kare apne aamaal par naaz kare aur apni ummeedo’n ka daaman phailaaye. Aur ham Tujh se panah maangte hai bure baatin aur chhote gunaho’n ko haqeer samajhne aur is baat se keh shaitaan ham par ghaalib aaye ya zamaana ham ko museebat mein phasaaye ya haakim apne zulm ka nishaana banaaye. Aur ham Tujh se panah maangte hai fuzool-kharchi mein padne, aur zaroorat-bhar rizq ke na milne se.", "Urdu": "ہم تجھ سے پناہ مانگتے ہیں اس بات سے کہ کسی کو فریب دینے کا قصد کریں یا اپنے اعمال پر نازاں ہوں اوراپنی امیدوں کا دامن پھیلائیں۔ اور ہم تجھ سے پناہ مانگتے ہیں بد باطنی اورچھوٹے گناہوں کوحقیر تصور کرنے اور اس بات سے کہ شیطان ہم پر غلبہ حاصل کر لے جائے یا زمانہ ہم کو مصیبت میں ڈالے یا فرمانروا اپنے مظالم کا نشانہ بنائے اورہم تجھ سے پناہ مانگتے ہیں فضول خرچی میں پڑنے،اورحسب ضرورت رزق کے نہ ملنے سے۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَنَعُوْذُ بِكَ اَنْ نَنْطَوِيَ عَلٰى غِشِّ اَحَدٍ وَاَنْ نُعْجِبَ بِاَعْمَالِنَا وَنَمُدَّ فِيْ اَمَالِنَا وَنَعُوْذُ بِكَ مِنْ سُوْۗءِ السَّرِيْرَةِ وَاحْتِقَارِ الصَّغِيْرَةِ وَاَنْ يَسْتَحْوِذَ عَلَيْنَا الشَّيْطَانُ اَوْ يَنْكُبَنَا الزَّمَانُ اَوْ يَتَهَضَّمَنَا السُّلْطَانُ وَنَعُوْذُ بِكَ مِنْ تَنَاوُلِ الْاِسْرَافِ وَمِنْ فِقْدَانِ الْكَفَافِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1001651, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "We seek refuge in Thee from the gloating of enemies, indigent need for equals, living in hardship, and dying without readiness. We seek refuge in Thee from the most dreadful remorse, the greatest affliction, the most wretched wretchedness, the evil end to the journey, the deprivation of reward, and the advent of punishment.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur ham Tujh se panah maangte hai dushmano ke mazaak udaane, ham-chashmo ki zaroorato’n, sakhti mein zindagi basar karne aur tosha'e aakherat (samaan'e aakherat) ke bagair mar jaane se. Aur Tujh se panah maangte hai bade afsos, badi museebat, bad-tareen bad-bakhti, bure anjaam, sawaab se mehroom aur azaab ke naazil hone se.", "Urdu": "ہم تجھ سے پناہ مانگتے ہیں دشمنوں کی شماتت،ہم چشموں کی احتیاج،سختی میں زندگی بسر کرنے اورتوشئہ آخرت کے بغیر مر جانے سے اور تجھ سے پناہ م